\id 1TI 1TU - Bible Iyansi 
\h 1 TUMÀTƐ 
\toc1 Un'kaan atàtwɛb akà Tumàtɛ 
\toc2 1 TUMÀTƐ 
\toc3 1Tm 
\mt2 Un'kaan atàtwɛb akà 
\mt1 Tumàtɛ 
\imt1 Nsɛmà 
\ip Un'kaan atàtwɛb akà Tumàtɛ Pɔl kàsön kà isii a 64 - 65 ungö a Yɛsu Klistɔ, u Masɛdwan a Filipe. 
\ip Pɔl kàmɛn mpay ntɔn Ikööŋ kàsɛmà nde u Ɛfɛsɔ, anà baar kàyisälà nde anà ba. Mpay ande yà naa u Ɛfɛsɔ yàkäl anà ndwà a nzam a itɛk anà an'lɔɔŋ a loor. Kyakin kàkwen nde muswaŋ isal ande akà mbuur a balàbal, wàŋàbuul mpem, awà kan'kwo mutüüb anà nde ntɔn mukyer isal mulɔŋ Ikööŋ a Nzam. 
\ip Isal abi nde kàkyer a Tumàtɛ, un'lɔŋki ande wà lää. Taarànde kàkäl Ungɛlɛki, ngwän kàkäl Un'yudà awà kàbulà un'klistɔ. Pɔl kàkwen naa Tumàtɛ udübà mun a baar a an'lɔɔŋ a loor anà ulɔŋ Ndaa a ndandaa. Baar bàkwen mukyer isal a ikyɛɛŋ, ba ban'sɔɔl isal a ntsà, muswaŋ nkääl a asyääl anà aseey. Tumàtɛ kàkäl umbɛy. Pɔl kàkwen naa baar bàkɔɔn un'bɛy, wɛɛ nde ukäl mbaan. 
\ip Un'kaan awà wàŋàyilà abà: - 1.1-2: Mbɔr - 1.3-11: An'lɔɔŋ a bunàbun mà Un'kɔɔn - 1.12-20: Imbäl ande - 2.1-3.13: Mɔ̈ɔ̈ a Ikööŋ - 3.14-4.5: An'lɔɔŋ a loor - 4.6-6.19: Asyääl a Nzam - 6.20-21: Ntsülà. 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Mbɔr 
\p  
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔl, ntööm a Klistɔ Yɛsu unsà nswɛɛŋ a Nzam awà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi anà Klistɔ Yɛsu awà làkyän abi. 
\p  
\v 2 Akà ngye Tumàtɛ, mwan amɛ wàndandaa unsà làkwikilà: Wɛy Taaràbi Nzam anà Mwol abi Klistɔ Yɛsu bapɛ kab angway, ndwääl a nkul anà duu. 
\s1 Ikyɛɛŋ ntɔn an'lɔɔŋ a loor 
\p  
\v 3 Mulab nswɛɛŋ kapɛ mɛ umpal kàlwomà mɛ u Masɛdwan, sàkal u Ɛfɛsɔ, ntɔn mutsuŋ baar bamwɛy mukɔɔn alɔŋ ndaa asin  
\v 4 anà mukɔɔn alab in'sim anà in'lwaaŋ mpa ifàtsü: mya myàfàtwaal nsyeel a mbaaŋ kikal mulab ukwen a Nzam abà bàfàkwo unsà làkwikilà.  
\v 5 Isin a nswɛɛŋ ayi kyà ukwen bàfàfà u mpem aŋàpɔŋà, unsà an'kyän aŋàbwaŋ anà làkwikilà a ndandaa.  
\v 6 Bumwɛy bàsàwɛy indiir abi, waa bàdiimà mbwo, bàkyàbulà muyisà in'lɔn ikɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ.  
\v 7 Ba bàfàkyey uyɔl naa ba bà alɔɔŋ a Un'kɔɔn, wɛɛ ba bàyöb anki itàkal indiir bàfàtɛn ba, itàkal ntɔn ndaa bàfàkyään ba a uyɔl banswà. 
\p  
\v 8 Bi ikyàyöb naa Un'kɔɔn wà ubwaŋ isàkal naa wa ban'syääl u mbwo aŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 9 Làyöb naa Un'kɔɔn bàkyer anki ntɔn ŋabalàbal, wɛɛ ntɔn aŋunkwɛm anà baar un'tswe ngwal, ntɔn baar mpa bàfàlab in'kɔɔn, baar abye anà mpem a kɔɔrà anà aŋaman'be, ntɔn baar bàfàbɛy Nzam anà indiir in'kyɛɛl, ntɔn baar bàfàdwa bàtaaràba anà bàngwän, ntɔn adwää baar anà  
\v 10 baar a ŋingyäy, ntɔn abaal bàfàbir ba a ba anà akaar bàfàbir ba a ba, ntɔn atɛɛl a yà a asɔ anà aŋaloor, ntɔn aŋimbäl a loor anà baar bàfàkyer undiir asin mpa ufàlab an'lɔɔŋ in'kyɛɛl.  
\v 11 An'lɔɔŋ amà mà uboo a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ alà ban'pɛ, alà làfü akà Nzam a làkɔɔ. 
\s1 An'tɔɔn ntɔn ubwaŋ a Nzam 
\p  
\v 12 Mɛ kan'fuur an'tɔɔn mbɔɔn akà Mwol abi Klistɔ Yɛsu awà kan'pɛ ngwal aŋàkwo, ntɔn nde kan'si mpem mpal kan'wɛl nde unsà isal ande,  
\v 13 mɛ mbuur kàkäl ŋambɛɛy, ŋamɛɛy a nkwaaŋ anà un'too a in'tswe. Wɛɛ nde kan'wem ngyɛb, ntɔn mɛ kàyöbà anki indiir kàkyɛrà mɛ ntɔn mɛ kàkäl anki anà làkwikilà.  
\v 14 Kab a ngway a Mwol abi làkäl aŋàsöönà akà mɛ, anà làkwikilà anà ukwen abà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu.  
\v 15 Ayi ndaa a làkwikilà ban'kwo baar banswà musà u mpem anà bàkyey ya naa Klistɔ Yɛsu kàyi u mɛɛn ntɔn mutswà bàŋan'be banswà mɔ̈ɔ̈. Mɛ, mɛ in'wà wàtàtwɛb uboo a ba.  
\v 16 Wɛɛ ntɔn abà, mɛ ban'wem ngyɛb, naa amu mɛ, mbuur atàtwɛb, Klistɔ Yɛsu uswɛŋ nkääŋ a mpem ande yanswa, asànaa mbaan ntɔn baar bàsàsà làkwikilà amu nde ntɔn mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye.  
\v 17 Akà Mfum a mbul a in'tye, mpa afàkwà, mpa afàmɛnà u mii, awà nde mpɛl Nzam, wɛy nsyäŋà anà làkoo ikäl anà nde ipepey! Abwɛy! 
\p  
\v 18 Mwan amɛ Tumàtɛ, le nswɛɛŋ amapà mɛ asànaa ngɔɔm bàtɛ itaan ntɔn ngye. Wɛy ndaa ayi ikäl ngwal a ngye unsà ità angye kyà ntsà,  
\v 19 kaar làkwikilà anà an'kyän aŋàbwaŋ. Bumwɛy bàkyàpiy an'kyän amà. Abun làkwikilà aba sye làkyàkyà bwà.  
\v 20 Uboo a baar abà bà Imɛnɛ anà Alɛksandre abà kàkäb mɛ akà Satanà ntɔn ba bàlɔŋkà mukɔɔn afàbɛy. 
\c 2  
\s1 Nswɛɛŋ ntɔn ngyamàkà 
\p  
\v 1 Kusà a indiir byanswà, mɛ kan'swaŋ naa bàtwab atàsà ndɔ̈ɔ̈m, ngyamàkà, mbɔ̈ɔ̈n, an'tɔɔn ntɔn baar banswà,  
\v 2 ntɔn amfum, anà baar abye anà ikɔ̈b, ntɔn bi ikäl anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ aŋàtɔlà mpem, wà duu unsà inzaam anà uyɔl banswà.  
\v 3 Abi indiir a ntsà ufàkyey Nzam awà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi,  
\v 4 awà akwen naa baar banswà bàwü mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà bàtöl muyɔ̈b ndandaa.  
\v 5 Ntɔn Nzam wà mwɛy, mfurboo mwɛy mpɛl uboo a Nzam anà baar, baal Klistɔ Yɛsu,  
\v 6 awà kàpɛ mɔ̈ɔ̈ ande ŋàkwo asànaa nkwiy ntɔn baar banswà. Abun, nde kàtɛ imbäl, umpal làkwe taaŋ.  
\v 7 Ntɔn abun mɛ, mɛ Nzam kan'si mukäl un'kyeey anà ntööm, un'lɔɔŋ a baar mpa abà Ayudà unsà làkwikilà anà ndandaa. Mɛ in'tà anki loor, wɛɛ mɛ an'tɛn ndandaa. 
\p  
\v 8 Abun, mɛɛ in'kwen naa abaal bàyamà kikal kyanswà, bàsɛɛn an'kɔɔ in'kyɛɛl u du, ukɔɔn nkyɛl anà an'sye. 
\p  
\v 9 Ntɔn akà akaar, wɛy ba bàbwäär ipfɛy aŋàbwaŋ mpa ipà nswɛn, ikɔɔn akal anà ntwɛn mbɔɔn. Wɛy ba bàkɔɔn atɔŋ ntswe, bàkɔɔn abwaar indiir a wɔl, an'yak, itàkal ipfɛy a ntal mbɔɔn,  
\v 10 wɛɛ, isal aŋàbwaŋ byan'kwo ntɔn akaar bàfàkyään inzaam.  
\v 11 Wɛy un'kaar uwɛl an'lwɛŋ a duu anà unkyeey wanswà. 
\p  
\v 12 Mɛ, mɛ impà anki mbwo akà un'kaar mulɔŋ, itàkal muwal ikɔ̈b udu a abaal. Wɛy nde ukäl unsà duu.  
\v 13 Ntɔn ya yà naa bàtàboom Adam kusà, Ɛva ungö.  
\v 14 Waa kà Adam anki bàkür, wɛɛ un'kaar, ungö bun'kür, nde kàbü u man'be.  
\v 15 Itàkal abun, nde asàwà mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a mböör a baan, isàkal naa nde wà uboo a làkwikilà, ukwen, un'kyɛɛl anà unsà làbɔ̈ɔ̈n. 
\c 3  
\s1 Aseey a Ikööŋ 
\p  
\v 1 Ndaa yi yà ndandaa: kya mbuur usàkal anà ngyal a isal a ikyɛɛŋ a Ikööŋ, nde kan'sɔɔl isal a ntsà.  
\v 2 Un'kyɛɛŋ a Ikööŋ akal mbuur akɔ̈ɔ̈n ifà ibe, un'dim a un'kyay mwɛy mpɛl, mbuur mpa awà ngaal, mbuur a duu, ŋambwäär aŋàbwaŋ, ŋun'kaay, mbuur kan'kwo mulɔŋ,  
\v 3 mpa awà un'yöör a man anà un'nwään a ngwiy, wɛɛ nde akal mbuur a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n anà ŋun'tüüb, mbuur mpa afàkwen ngim mbɔɔn.  
\v 4 Wɛy nde ukäl aŋàkwo muyaal ndwà ande ŋàkwo anà mukyer naa baan ande bàkäl unsà unkyeey anà làzir lanswà.  
\v 5 Lalan, kya mbuur uyöb anki muler ndwà ande ŋàkwo, nde ayàkwo aben muler Ikööŋ a Nzam?  
\v 6 Nde ukwo anki mukal mbuur akün unsà mbuul a mpem, naa tɛy, nde ayàsɛɛn an'pɛy, waa uyàwal mbar asànaa kàwɛl ileŋ.  
\v 7 Wɛy sye naa baar abà u nsà a Ikööŋ bun'tɛɛl imbäl aŋàbwaŋ, ntɔn nde ukɔ̈ɔ̈n abwà u nswɛn anà unsà intaam a ileŋ. 
\s1 Asyääl a Ikööŋ 
\p  
\v 8 Ifà imwɛy sye, asyääl bàkal baar a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n anà bà mpem mwɛy. Ba bàkal anki ayɔ̈ɔ̈r a man anà baar bàfàkal anà ilään a bweel a nswɛn.  
\v 9 Wɛy ba bàkäär ngyee a làkwikilà unsà an'kyän aŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 10 Yubwaŋ naa bàtwab atàsi, ungö, isàkal naa undiir un'be bàmɛn anki amu ba, apan waa ba bàsal.  
\v 11 Akaar sye bàkal baar a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n, mpa bàfàtwee, baar a duu, bàfasyeel mpem unsà indiir byanswà.  
\v 12 Asyääl a Ikööŋ abaal bàkal adim a un'kyay mwɛy mpɛl anà bàkyer ayöb muyaal baan aba anà ndwà aba ŋakwo.  
\v 13 Ntɔn asyääl bàfàkyer isal aba ubwaŋàbwaŋ bàfàwal làkoo anà uyɔl byan'fà unsà làkwikilà amu Klistɔ Yɛsu. 
\s1 Ngyee a kölàköl 
\p  
\v 14 Amasöön mɛ indiir abi, ntɔn mɛ an'sà làkyän naa mɛ in'kyer ayàlaler ungö a kitaaŋ.  
\v 15 Itàkal abun, kya mɛ in'sàlam muyà, ngye akyer ayàyɔ̈b naa nkääl angye ikal aben u ndwà a Nzam, ayà Ikɔ̈ɔ̈ŋ a Nzam a mɔ̈ɔ̈, ta a ndwà anà un'käär a ndandaa.  
\v 16 Ukɔɔn mbaaŋ, Ngyee unsà inzaam yà kölàköl! Klistɔ: 
\q1 kàyàmɛnà asànaa mbuur, 
\q1 Dweelà In'kyɛɛl kun'twey wàbalàbal, 
\q1 nde kàyàmɛnà akà akyeey a Nzam. 
\q1 Nde bàkyään akà in'sɛŋ myumwɛy, 
\q1 bun'si làkwikilà u mɛɛn, 
\q1 nde bun'sɛɛn unsà làkɔɔ! 
\c 4  
\s1 An'lɔɔŋ an'be 
\p  
\v 1 Dweelà làtɛɛnà ubwaŋàbwaŋ naa kan'taaŋ a ntsüü, amwɛy bàsàpiy làkwikilà ntɔn mulab an'dweelà a loor anà an'lɔɔŋ man'fà akà insɔŋà.  
\v 2 Mpem yweel a baar a loor isabwiy ndwaŋ. An'kyän aba màŋàbwà bwoor.  
\v 3 Baar aban bàfàtsuŋ baar mutà bɔr anà mudyà isaa byumwɛy. Wɛɛ Nzam bya kàkyer ntɔn aŋàlàkwikilà abà bàyöb ndandaa ubwaŋàbwaŋ bàdi bya unsà mfuur a an'tɔɔn.  
\v 4 Ntɔn indiir byanswà kàkyer Nzam byàŋàbwaŋ, undiir a piy bwà watɛy isàkal naa wa ban'wal unsà mfuur a an'tɔɔn,  
\v 5 ntɔn wa wàŋàkyɛɛl u mbwo a Ndaa a Nzam anà ngyamàkà. 
\s1 Un'syääl a Klistɔ Yɛsu wàŋàbwaŋ 
\p  
\v 6 Kyään indiir abi akà atɔŋ: abun ngye ayàkal un'syääl a Klistɔ Yɛsu wàŋàbwaŋ, wàŋàyuur a ndaa a làkwikilà anà an'lɔɔŋ a ntsà kàläb ngye ubwaŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 7 Tɔn nsim mpa ifàlab làkwikilà, itaŋà a anün akaar. Wɛɛ lɔŋàkà inzaam.  
\v 8 An'taam mupà ndür ngwal mà mfun unsà indiir ikikye, wɛɛ inzaam kyà mfun unsà indiir byanswà. Ntɔn kya ifàpà ilää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ aŋàbà anà kyà mɔ̈ɔ̈ ayàyà.  
\v 9 Ndaa ayi yà ndandaa ayà ban'kwo baar banswà musyeel mpem.  
\v 10 Lalan, isàkal naa bi imanà mpay anà inwaanà ntɔn ya, ntɔn bi kàkyàsà làkyän amu Nzam a mɔ̈ɔ̈ awà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ a baar banswà, sin sin aŋàlàkwikilà. 
\p  
\v 11 Swaŋ indiir abi anà lɔŋ bya.  
\v 12 Wɛy mbuur mwɛy ukɔ̈ɔ̈n abɛy imbɛy angye! Wɛɛ ngye kal mbaan akà aŋàlàkwikilà u ntɛɛn, u nkääl, unsà ukwen, u làkwikilà, anà u mpem aŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 13 Apà in'yàyà mɛ, sà muküünà mutaŋ Ndaa Aŋàsɔn, mulɛɛl anà mulɔŋ.  
\v 14 Twon an'bɛy kab a ngway alà amu ngye, alà bapɛ u mbwo a ngɔɔm anà nsyeel a an'kɔɔ a andweer.  
\v 15 Pà mpem angye unsà indiir abi, pà mɔ̈ɔ̈ angye wanswà unsà isal angye, waa baar banswà bàyàman naa isal angye kyàmukyà usà.  
\v 16 Kal kà igyɛɛŋ ntɔn ngye ŋakwo anà ntɔn alɔɔŋ angye. Kal aŋàtsim unsà indiir abi byanswà. Kya ngye asàkyer abun, ngye ayàtswà mɔ̈ɔ̈ angye ŋakwo anà wà baar bàfaweem. 
\c 5  
\s1 Nsyääl ntɔn aŋàlàkwikilà 
\p  
\v 1 Twon aŋän a ngwal baal aŋànün, wɛɛ un'lɛɛl asànaa taaràŋà. Awɛl atö asànaa atɔŋ,  
\v 2 andweer akaar asànaa bàmaa, asyee asànaa ampääŋ, unsà mpem aŋàbwaŋ. 
\p  
\v 3 Asyäŋà akweel adim, akweel adim abà bàndandaa aŋàyen.  
\v 4 Wɛɛ, isàkal naa un'kweel un'dim mwɛy we anà baan itàkal atil, wɛy ba bàtwab atàlɔŋkà musyääl làkwikilà aba u ndwà aba ŋakwo anà mufuur ibay akà aböör aba. Awà undiir ufàkyey Nzam.  
\v 5 Un'kweel un'dim a ndandaa awà aŋàyen, afàsà làkyän ande amu Nzam. Nde afàsin aküünà u ndɔ̈ɔ̈m anà u ngyamàkà mpib anà mwäänà.  
\v 6 Wɛɛ, wunà akwà afàsyääl ilään a ndür, nde wàŋàkwà itaan, itàkal naa nde wà anà mɔ̈ɔ̈.  
\v 7 Le indiir atsuŋ ngye ba, ntɔn ba bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n apɛl.  
\v 8 Isàkal naa mbuur ufàbay anki atɔŋ ande, sin sin baar a ndwà ande, nde kan'kɔɔb làkwikilà ande, nde kan'söön mbuur akɔ̈ɔ̈n làkwikilà unsà ube. 
\p  
\v 9 Musɔn ikɔb a un'kaar unsà itsuŋ a akweel adim, nde akal àŋàkölà mbul an'kwem an'syaam, anà kàkäl un'kyay a un'dim mwɛy mpɛl.  
\v 10 Wɛy nde ukäl un'kaar awà bàyöb isal ande byà ntsà: kàbɔɔŋ baan ande ubwaŋàbwaŋ, kàfawalà baar u ndwà ande, kàfaywɛyà in'kɔl a aŋàlàkwikilà, kàbayà aŋangyɛb anà kàfakyerà undiir wanswà wàŋàbwaŋ. 
\p  
\v 11 Wɛɛ akà akweel adim abà asyee, twon an'kyey mukasɔn. Ntɔn, umpal ifàsɛnà ilään a ndür aba, ya ifasiinà mufàbääl, waa bàkɔɔb Klistɔ,  
\v 12 abun, ba ban'bwà unsà ikwàndwà ntɔn ban'bɛy ba kyään aba làtàtwɛb.  
\v 13 Apan sye, ntɔn ubwal, ba bàfàlɔŋkà muyikyà ndwà a ndwà. Yan'söön ube, ba kà nà abwal mpɛl anki, wɛɛ sye baar a itetɛɛn anà bà mun ipɔl.  
\v 14 Abun, mɛ in'kwen naa akweel adim abà asyee bàtɛ bɔr, bàbör baan, bàyaal ndwà aba anà bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n apà abör mbwo atwee.  
\v 15 Ntɔn amwɛy amu ba bàfuràtàdiimà mbwo ntɔn mulab Satanà.  
\v 16 Isàkal naa ŋàlàkwikilà mwɛy we anà akweel adim u ywar ande, wɛy nde kabay, waa buur bàkɔɔn akal udu a Ikööŋ, ntɔn Ikööŋ ikwe mubay akweel adim abà ndandaa aŋàyen. 
\p  
\v 17 Andweer bàfàler Ikööŋ ubwaŋàbwaŋ ban'kwo muwal nsyäŋà mbalà yweel, sin sin ba akwà bàfàwal buur a kölàköl unsà Ndaa anà an'lɔɔŋ.  
\v 18 Abun, Ndaa Aŋàsɔn itɛɛnà naa: « Twon an'bäm mun a ngɔɔmà utaaŋ undyarà wa mbɛŋ » anà: « Un'syääl an'kwo muwal làfur ande. »  
\v 19 Twon an'kyey mfüün ntɔn un'dweer ukɔɔn imbäl a baar bɔ̈ɔ̈l itàkal atär.  
\v 20 Baar ban'kyer man'be, aŋän u mii a baar banswà, ntɔn bumwɛy sye bàmɛn bɔɔmà. 
\p  
\v 21 Mɛ amalɔɔm umii a Nzam, u mii a Klistɔ Yɛsu anà u mii a akyeey in'kyɛɛl: lab indiir abi ukɔɔn nkyɛɛr anà ukɔɔn un'kɔl aŋàyɔŋ.  
\v 22 Twon an'düül musà mbuur an'kɔɔ, twon an'bilà unsà man'be a mbuur asin. Ngye ŋakwo kal wàŋàpöŋà. 
\p  
\v 23 Wɛy munwà an'dà mpɛl, wɛɛ nwà sye ndam a man, ntɔn kwiy angye anà an'kyal angye taaŋ lanswà. 
\p  
\v 24 Man'be a baar amwɛy màfàmɛnà kusà mutsul mbar, wɛɛ akà bumwɛy, ma màfàmɛnà ungöngö.  
\v 25 Abun sye, isal a ntsà byàkyer afàmɛnà, itàkal bya akwà mpa byàfàmɛnà agyä byàkwo anki musin akalà byàŋàyee. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Wɛy baar banswà abà asɔ bàkyey naa ankum aba ban'kwo muwal nsyäŋà aŋàkwo, ntɔn mbuur ukɔ̈ɔ̈n abɛy ikɔb a Nzam anà an'lɔɔŋ abi.  
\v 2 Isàkal naa ankum aba bà aŋàlàkwilà, ba bàkwo anki mukabɛy naa ntɔn ba bà atɔŋ. Wɛɛ, wɛy ba basyääl aŋàsöön ubwaŋ, ntɔn baar bàwal bweel a nsyääl aba yàŋàbwaŋ bà aŋàlàkwikilà anà nkween. Indiir abi lɔŋ bya anà swaŋ bya. 
\s1 An'lɔɔŋ a loor anà in'naaŋ a ndandaa 
\p  
\v 3 Isàkal naa mbuur kan'lɔŋ ndaa asin, anà kan'kɔɔn alab ndaa a ndandaa a Mwol abi Klistɔ Yɛsu anà an'lɔɔŋ a inzaam,  
\v 4 nde wàŋàyɔl a uyɔl, wà insil, wà ŋukyal ntɔn nsyeel a mbaaŋ anà ngwiy a ngɔk, indiir byàfàtwaal un'köl, an'sye, in'tswe, an'kyän an'be,  
\v 5 anà mbaaŋ mpa ifàtsü uboo a baar aŋun'yɛnà aŋàkalà, mpa abye anà ndandaa. Ba bàfàsi naa inzaam kyà mbwo muwal bweel. 
\p  
\v 6 Yà ndandaa naa inzaam kyà bweel a kölàköl akà mbuur afàman un'sak unsà indiir awe nde abya.  
\v 7 Ntɔn bi kàtwääl anki akundiir mwɛy u mɛɛn mà, bi sye ikwe anki mufàsyen undiir kan'fà mwo.  
\v 8 Abun, isàkal naa bi ibye anà isaa anà ipfɛy, bya byan'kwo ntɔn bi.  
\v 9 Wɛɛ akà baar bàfàkwen mukal aŋin'naaŋ, ba bàfàbwà u ndɛb, unsà untaam, anà unsà in'lään mbɔɔn myà upool anà myube, amyà ifàmiin baar u mpay anà kukwà.  
\v 10 Ntɔn ukwen a ngim bisin a mpay yanswà. Bamwɛy bàbilà afwee mwo, bàkyàdiimà mbwo a làkwikilà, anà bàkyàpɛɛl usaay mbɔɔn ba ŋakwo. 
\s1 Nswɛɛŋ akà Tumàtɛ 
\p  
\v 11 Wɛɛ ngye, mbuur a Nzam, tiin indiir abi, waa aleŋ balàbal, inzaam, làkwikilà, ukwen, nkääŋ a mpem, duu.  
\v 12 Nwan ità aŋàbwaŋ kyà làkwikilà. Kaar mɔ̈ɔ̈ a mbul a in'tye awà babel mukyey mpal kàtɛ ngye imbäl a ntsà kyà làkwikilà u mii a ambäl mbɔɔn.  
\v 13 Mɛ amaswaŋ u mii a Nzam awà afàpà mɔ̈ɔ̈ akindiir byanswà, anà u mii a Klistɔ Yɛsu awà kàtɛ imbäl ande kyà ntsà u mii a Pɔnsi Pilatu naa:  
\v 14 Lab nswɛɛŋ ukɔɔn mbiin anà ukɔɔn pɛl, tii mpal usyemɛnà Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 15 Mɛɛnà ayi isàkal u taaŋ kàsi ŋun'sak, awà nde mpɛl udu a indiir byanswà, Mfum a amfum, Mwol a amwol.  
\v 16 Nde mpɛl mpà afàkwà, awà afàkal u pɛɛlà mwɛy mpa kan'kwo mbuur mwɛy musin tsütsü apà la. Akà mbuur mwɛy kun'mɛn anki anà ukwo anki mukun'man. Làkoo anà ngwal a mbul a in'tye ye anà nde! Wöwöö! 
\p  
\v 17 Aswɛŋ aŋin'naaŋ a mɛɛn mà bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n asɛɛn an'pɛy anà bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n asà làkyän aba unsà in'naaŋ mpa myàfàlam, wɛɛ amu Nzam, awà afipà un'kàbɔ a indiir, ntɔn bi imɛn un'sak unsà bya.  
\v 18 Aswɛŋ ba bàkyer yàŋàbwaŋ, bàkäl aŋin'naaŋ unsà isal a ntsà, bàkäl aŋun'kääb, aŋun'tüüb.  
\v 19 Abun, ba bàsàköŋà un'naaŋ a ntsà anà wàngwal ntɔn taaŋ làsàyà ungö, ntɔn musàwal mɔ̈ɔ̈ a ndandaa. 
\p  
\v 20 Ɔ Tumàtɛ, kaar ubwaŋàbwaŋ an'lɔɔŋ manswà bapɛ. Tiin an'yääm màkɔ̈ɔ̈n ndöŋ anà mpa màfàlab làkwikilà, anà mbaaŋ ayà un'yɛnà un'be.  
\v 21 Baar amwɛy abà bàswɛŋ ngaal naa ba bye anà un'yenà un'be awà, ba bàkyàdiimà mbwo a làkwikilà. Wɛy kab a ngway a Nzam làkäl anä ngye!